de.unifrankfurt.informatik.acoli.starling.types

Class StarlingReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.unifrankfurt.informatik.acoli.starling.types.StarlingReference

  • public class StarlingReference
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for representing bibliographic references as used in the REFERENCE field in the XML export of a Starling dictionary.

    Example : Parse XML REFERENCE into StarlingReference

    <field name="REFERENCE">ЭСТЯ 6, 9-10, VEWT 275 (should be distinguished from PT *Kob-).</field>

    Reference 1 :
    ShortNameId = ЭСТЯ
    pageRange = 9-10
    comment =

    Reference 2 :
    ShortNameId = VEWT
    pageRange = 275
    comment = (should be distinguished from PT *Kob-)

    Author:
    frank
